<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="<%templateskin%>/css/base.css" />
	
		<link href="<%templateskin%>/css/mui.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<link href="<%templateskin%>/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<title>充值</title>
		<style>
			.mui-toast-container{
				bottom: 50%;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
        <%if(action=="confirm")%>
        <form id="pay_form" name="pay_form" method="get" action="{config.webpath}api/payment/{payModel.api_path}/index.aspx" target="_blank">
            <input id="pay_order_no" name="pay_order_no" type="hidden" value="{order_no}" />
            <input id="pay_order_amount" name="pay_order_amount" type="hidden" value="{order_amount}" />
            <input id="pay_user_name" name="pay_user_name" type="hidden" value="{userModel.user_name}" />
            <dd class="wrap-box">
                <dl>
                    <dt>支付金额</dt>
                    <dd>￥{order_amount}</dd>
                </dl>
                <dl>
                    <dt>支付方式</dt>

                    <dd>
                        {payModel.title}
                    </dd>

                </dl>
                <input id="pay_subject" name="pay_subject" type="hidden" value="购买商品" />

                <div style="padding:0 0 15px 0;">
                    <input id="btnSubmit" name="btnSubmit" type="submit" value="确认付款" class="btn red full" />
                </div>
        </form>

        <%/if%>

        <%if(action=="succeed")%>
        <!--支付成功-->
        <div class="wrap-box">
            <h2>支付成功</h2>
            <div class="tip">
                <span class="icon check"></span>
                <p>恭喜您，您的支付已经成功！</p>
                <p>您可以点击这里进入<a name="<%linkurl(" usercenter","index")%>" data-ignore="true">会员中心</a>查看订单状态！</p>
                <p>如有其它问题，请立即与我们客服人员联系。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--/支付成功-->
        <%/if%>

        <%if(action=="error")%>
        <!--支付出错-->
        <div class="wrap-box">
            <h2>支付失败</h2>
            <div class="tip">
                <span class="icon close"></span>
                <p>支付过程中发生意处错误！</p>
                <p>您可以点击这里进入<a name="<%linkurl(" usercenter","index")%>" data-ignore="true">会员中心</a>查看订单状态！</p>
                <p>如您确实已经支付，请与我们客服人员联系。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--/支付出错-->
        <%/if%>

        <%if(action=="login")%>
        <!--用户未登录-->
        <div class="wrap-box">
            <h2>会员登录</h2>
            <div class="tip">
                <span class="icon info"></span>
                <p>您尚未登录或已经超时啦！</p>
                <p>已是会员用户，请<a name="<%linkurl(" login")%>" data-ignore="true">点击这里登录</a>。</p>
                <p>尚未注册会员，请<a name="<%linkurl(" register")%>" data-ignore="true">点击这里注册</a>。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--/用户未登录-->
        <%/if%>

        <%if(action=="recharge")%>
        <!--用户余额不足-->
        <div class="wrap-box">
            <h2>余额不足</h2>
            <div class="tip">
                <span class="icon warning"></span>
                <p>对不起，您的余额不足本次支付！</p>
                <p>如余额不足，请<a class="close-popup" name="<%linkurl(" userwallet")%>" data-ignore="true">点击这里充值</a>后进行支付！</p>
                <p>如果有任何问题，请与我们客服取得联系。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--/用户余额不足-->
        <%/if%>
	</body>
	<script src="<%templateskin%>/js/jquery-3.0.0.min.js"></script>
	<script src="<%templateskin%>/js/mui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="<%templateskin%>/js/common.js"></script>
	<script>
		//MUI框架初始化
		mui.init();
		
	
		
		
</script>
</html>
